<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_330_r1l3">Lieber Steffan vnd <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde Als vvir ew vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
